Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
The obvious patterns indicating a non-linear relationship between \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]IPO Size\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] and the dependent \
variable as well as the one indicating a negative correlation between the \
variance of the dependent variable and \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]announcement \
timing\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] have disappeared. The log-transformation seems \
to have worked in both cases.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8679149968938847`*^9, 
  3.8679151112080603`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"804624bf-2edf-4d6b-a2f0-\
1a869229f39c"],

